 &  &  &  & \uparrow &  & F_{A} & \searrow\\
\mathbf{x} & \overset{F_{A}}{\rightarrow} & \mathbf{A}(\mathbf{x}) & \rightarrow & \otimes &  &  &  & \mathbf{A}(\mathbf{y})\\
